# Superdesk API

# Group users

## GET /user/{id}
Returns a specific user by id.

+ Parameters
        + id (required, number, `1`)

+ Response 200

    ```js
    {
        _link_self: '/user/1',
        _create_time: '',
        _update_time: '',
        _is_active: true,
        _permissions: {
            read: true,
            update: true
        },
        first_name: 'karel',
        last_name: 'badlik',
        user_name: 'kbadlik',
        email: 'kbadlik@gmail.com',
        info: {skype: 'karel.badlik', phone: '+420 777 77 77'}
    }
    ```

